comments: Huerter (ATL) engages and disengages with Neto (WAS) as the pick is set.
Capela (ATL) is moving slightly forward as Hachimura (WAS) jumps toward the rim and marginal body contact occurs during Hachimura's upward shooting motion.
Hachimura (WAS) brings his off-arm toward Capela's (ATL) left arm and marginal contact occurs as Capela contests the layup attempt.

Gafford (WAS) places his left arm against Capela (ATL) and marginal contact occurs as he collapses his arm.  Capela loses control of the ball and Gafford makes incidental contact with his hand after the ball is loose.
Huerter (ATL) turns alongside Westbrook's (WAS) path and absorbs the marginal body contact that occurs at the end of the drive.
Westbrook (WAS) brings his off-arm toward Huerter's (ATL) front as he slows his forward momentum and marginal contact occurs as he naturally releases away.
Bertans (WAS) makes clean contact with the ball and dislodges it away from Collins (ATL) before incidental contact occurs during the rebound.
Collins (ATL) and Gafford (WAS) engage and disengage with one another off-ball.
Hachimura (WAS) splits his feet at the start of his dribble.
Bertans (WAS) extends his hand forward toward Young's (ATL) front and marginal contact occurs during Young's drive into the lane.
Bertans (WAS) legally contests Young's (ATL) driving shot attempt.
Hachimura (WAS) gathers the ball and legally takes two steps to the basket.
Collins (ATL) firms up in his screening position in Bertans' (WAS) path and absorbs the contact.
Westbrook (WAS) initiates contact across Collins' (ATL) left arm during his upward shooting motion.
Capela (ATL) and Gafford (WAS) engage and disengage with one another as Gafford sets the screen during the inbound.
Bogdanovic (ATL) and Bertans (WAS) engage and disengage with one another along the perimeter.
Huerter (ATL) turns into Westbrook (WAS) and delivers contact to Westbrook's side after his gather. Huerter then initiates further contact with Westbrook's left shoulder during his upward motion.
Collins (ATL) establishes himself in a screening position in Neto's (WAS) path and absorbs the contact.
Neto (WAS) swipes down and cleanly dislodges the ball before incidental arm contact occurs with Collins (ATL).
Gafford (WAS) and Collins (ATL) make incidental body contact with one another during rebounding.
Bogdanovic (ATL) legally contests Westbrook's (WAS) jump shot attempt.
